{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'指甲彩繪 DIY 套組熱銷，凝膠指甲燈與貼片式美甲受歡迎',p:'美甲沙龍費用上漲推動 DIY 美甲需求。UV/LED 凝膠指甲燈、半固化凝膠貼片、美甲工具組搜尋量年增 35%。ohora 與 Beetles 品牌在 Amazon 上銷量領先。$15-30 入門套組最受歡迎。',src:'https://www.bebolddigital.com/blog/top-amazon-categories-2026',products:['Beetles Gel Nail Polish Kit with UV Light','ohora Semi Cured Gel Nail Strips','Modelones Gel Nail Polish Starter Kit']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'Clean Beauty 認證成為購買決策關鍵，EWG 評分影響轉換率',p:'消費者越來越重視成分安全。EWG Verified、Leaping Bunny（無動物實驗）、Vegan 認證產品在 Amazon 上獲得更高轉換率。「成分透明」成為品牌差異化關鍵。Paraben-free、Sulfate-free 是基本要求。',src:'https://supplykick.com/blog/amazon-beauty-trends',products:['Drunk Elephant Protini Polypeptide Cream','Herbivore Botanicals Blue Tansy Mask','Pacifica Beauty Vegan Collagen Serum']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'美容工具與配件利潤率高，冰球滾輪與 Gua Sha 持續熱銷',p:'美容工具利潤率通常高於護膚品。玉石 Gua Sha、冰球滾輪、矽膠洗臉刷是長青熱銷品。$8-20 價位帶衝動購買率高。禮盒包裝版本在節日季銷量翻倍。',src:'https://junglescout.com/blog/amazon-product-trends/',products:['BAIMEI Jade Roller & Gua Sha Set','Ice Roller for Face & Eye Puffiness','FOREO LUNA 4 Mini Facial Cleansing Brush']}
