{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'TWS 耳機平價替代品銷量驚人，Qi2 認證成為新賣點',p:'AirPods 替代品（$20-40）銷量驚人。MagSafe 相容無線充電板、車用無線充電支架持續熱銷。Apple Watch 錶帶、AirPods 保護殼等品牌配件平價替代品市場龐大。Qi2 無線充電標準正在成為新標準。',src:'https://salesduo.com/blog/amazon-trends-for-2026/',products:['Soundcore by Anker Space A40 Earbuds','Anker MagSafe Wireless Charging Pad','Spigen Rugged Armor AirPods Pro 2 Case']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'降噪耳機需求穩定成長，ANC 功能從高階下放到 $50 以下價位',p:'主動降噪（ANC）功能從 $200+ 高階耳機下放到 $30-50 價位帶。通勤、辦公、旅行場景推動需求。Sony WF-1000XM5 與 AirPods Pro 2 穩居高階市場。平價 ANC 耳機成長更快。',src:'https://explodingtopics.com/blog/trending-products',products:['Sony WF-1000XM5 Wireless Earbuds','Apple AirPods Pro 2nd Generation','Soundcore by Anker Liberty 4 NC']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'Apple Watch 錶帶市場龐大，第三方替代品銷量遠超原廠',p:'Apple Watch 第三方錶帶市場龐大。矽膠運動錶帶、不鏽鋼米蘭錶帶、尼龍編織錶帶是三大熱銷款式。$5-15 價位帶銷量最高。多色組合包（3-5 條）轉換率高於單條。',src:'https://whop.com/blog/amazon-trends/',products:['WFEAGL Apple Watch Band Silicone 4-Pack','Fullmosa Apple Watch Band Stainless Steel','Apple Watch Ultra Nylon Loop Band']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'MagSafe 配件生態系持續擴張，磁吸式卡夾與支架是新爆品',p:'MagSafe 磁吸式卡夾、磁吸式支架、磁吸式行動電源搜尋量年增 35%。iPhone 用戶對 MagSafe 生態系的接受度持續提升。$10-30 價位帶配件利潤率高。Android 陣營也開始支援 Qi2 磁吸。',src:'https://salesduo.com/blog/amazon-trends-for-2026/',products:['MOFT Snap-On Phone Stand & Wallet','ESR HaloLock MagSafe Wallet Stand','Anker 622 MagGo Magnetic Battery']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'藍牙喇叭市場成熟但需求穩定，防水與便攜性是關鍵賣點',p:'JBL、Bose、Sony 品牌主導藍牙喇叭市場。IPX7 防水、12 小時+ 電池續航、USB-C 充電是消費者基本要求。$30-80 價位帶銷量最高。戶外與旅行場景推動便攜式喇叭需求。',src:'https://www.accio.com/business/amazon-best-selling-wireless',products:['JBL Flip 6 Portable Bluetooth Speaker','Bose SoundLink Flex Bluetooth Speaker','Ultimate Ears WONDERBOOM 3']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'無線充電多設備充電站需求上升，3-in-1 充電座受 Apple 用戶歡迎',p:'iPhone + Apple Watch + AirPods 三合一無線充電座搜尋量年增 30%。Belkin 與 Anker 品牌在 Amazon 上領先。$30-60 價位帶成長最快。桌面整潔與減少線材是主要購買動機。',src:'https://www.darkroomagency.com/observatory/which-amazon-product-categories-are-growing-in-2025',products:['Belkin BoostCharge Pro 3-in-1 Wireless Charger','Anker 3-in-1 Cube MagSafe Charger','ESR 3-in-1 MagSafe Charging Station']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'骨傳導耳機從運動專用走向日常，開放式聆聽成為新趨勢',p:'骨傳導耳機讓用戶在聽音樂時仍能聽到環境音。跑步、騎車、辦公場景推動需求。Shokz（原 AfterShokz）品牌主導市場。$80-130 價位帶成長最快。開放式耳機（Open Ear）也在成長。',src:'https://www.bebolddigital.com/blog/top-amazon-categories-2026',products:['Shokz OpenRun Pro 2 Bone Conduction','Shokz OpenFit Air Open-Ear Earbuds','Bose Ultra Open Earbuds']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'手機殼與保護貼是 Wireless 品類最大子品類，新機發布帶動換購潮',p:'每年 iPhone/Samsung 新機發布帶動手機殼與保護貼換購潮。MagSafe 相容、軍規防摔、透明設計是三大熱門款式。$8-20 價位帶銷量最高。Spigen、TORRAS、Caseology 品牌在 Amazon 上領先。',src:'https://junglescout.com/blog/amazon-product-trends/',products:['Spigen Ultra Hybrid MagSafe iPhone 16 Case','TORRAS Slim Fit iPhone 16 Pro Case','amFilm Glass Screen Protector iPhone 16']},
{t:'📈 趨勢',h:'智慧手錶配件市場穩定，充電線與保護殼是高回購品',p:'Apple Watch、Samsung Galaxy Watch、Garmin 手錶的充電線、保護殼、螢幕保護貼是穩定需求品。$5-15 價位帶衝動購買率高。新款手錶發布後配件銷量在 2-4 週內爆發。',src:'https://helium10.com/blog/amazon-wireless-trends',products:['Apple Watch Magnetic Charging Cable','Misxi Apple Watch Case with Screen Protector','Samsung Galaxy Watch Charging Dock']}
